additional_information: Erectile Dysfunction or ED happens when a penis owner has ongoing problems getting and keeping an erection. Without treatment, ED can make sex difficult. The problem is commonly reported by 1 in 5 men and may increase with age.
diagnosis: You are recommended to increase frequency of sexual activity.
general_advice: Increasing the frequency of your erections may help you in better erections.
causes: Some of the common causes of erectile dysfunction may include- Injury in the penis ‚Ä¢ Prostrate surgery ‚Ä¢ Surgery in the spinal cord ‚Ä¢ Diabetes ‚Ä¢ Low testosterone ‚Ä¢ High blood pressure ‚Ä¢ Neurological disorders ‚Ä¢ Cardiovascular disorder ‚Ä¢ Psychological factors like depression, anxiety, performance anxiety, stress poor self-concept, relationship issue with partner ‚Ä¢ Lack of privacy ‚Ä¢ Side-effect of certain medication for treating depression, anxiety and high blood pressure ‚Ä¢ Lifestyle factors- drug abuse, alcohol abuse and smoking.
